																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">3</div> <div class="vers-content">And you have respect to him that is clothed with the fine apparel, and shall say to him: Sit thou here well; but say to the poor man: Stand thou there, or sit under my footstool:</div></div></td>
