																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">13</div> <div class="vers-content">For judgment without mercy to him that hath not done mercy. And mercy exalteth itself above judgment.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">13</div> <div class="vers-content">The merciless will be judged mercilessly; mercy gives its judgement an honourable welcome.  </div></div></td>
