																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">23</div> <div class="vers-content">And the scripture was fulfilled, saying: Abraham believed God, and it was reputed to him to justice, and he was called the friend of God.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">23</div> <div class="vers-content">Thus he confirmed the words of scripture, which tell us, Abraham put his faith in God, and it was reckoned virtue in him, and he earned the title of Godâ€™s friend. </div></div></td>
